clusters.neutral_headline: Wales host Bosnia and NI visit Italy in World Cup play-offs

items.title: Wales host Bosnia and NI visit Italy in World Cup play-offs
items.standfirst: Wales will host Bosnia-Herzegovina and Northern Ireland travel to Italy in the World Cup play-off semi-finals.
items.content: Wales will host Bosnia-Herzegovina and Northern Ireland travel to Italy in the World Cup play-off semi-finals.

items.title: Wales, Northern Ireland and the Republic of Ireland find out World Cup play-off opponents
items.standfirst: Northern Ireland have been drawn to play Italy in the semi-finals of the World Cup play-offs, while Wales face Bosnia and Herzegovina and the Republic of Ireland take on the Czech Republic.
items.content: Northern Ireland have been drawn to play Italy in the semi-finals of the World Cup play-offs, while Wales face Bosnia and Herzegovina and the Republic of Ireland take on the Czech Republic.
